top_projects.name: genetic_mutation
top_projects.description: This project focuses on using machine learning to classify genetic mutations as drivers or passengers in cancer tumors, automating a process currently done manually by clinical pathologists. This aims to enhance precision medicine using genetic data.

top_projects.name: diabetes_ann
top_projects.description: Implemented an advanced artificial neural network (ANN) model utilizing Keras to predict diabetes onset, leveraging techniques such as data normalization, hyperparameter optimization, and multi-layer perceptron architecture. The project involved comprehensive data analysis and rigorous evaluation through ROC curve

top_projects.name: breastcan
top_projects.description: This project focuses on building a Breast Cancer Detection system using machine learning techniques. The system analyzes input medical data, such as tumor characteristics, to predict whether a tumor is malignant or benign. It leverages supervised learning algorithms to provide accurate predictions and assist in early cancer diagnosis.

top_projects.name: counter-fitness
top_projects.description: This project utilizes OpenCV and MediaPipe to track and count bicep curls and push-ups in a workout video. It calculates the angle of the elbow joint, displays the number of repetitions, visualizes the progress with a bar indicator, and shows real-time FPS.

top_projects.name: email
top_projects.description: The AI Email Marketing Tool is designed to help companies craft personalized, impactful emails for potential clients. By analyzing a company's existing case studies and comparing them with prospective clients' profiles, the tool generates tailored email content that highlights successes and suggests strategies to boost the prospect's business
